Remember this is just an entry-level tutorial. With the programmable transaction feature, you should be able to implement many different interesting functions on your DApp in a blockchain-native way.

If you have any confusion while using Razor wallet kit, please check out the docs of Razor wallet kit.

If you find any issues or bugs, welcome to submit issues or PRs to the Github repo. Let's make Movement and open-source community better together!

